---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Recharge &amp; Bill Payments | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Recharge &amp; Bills</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Recharge &amp; Bill Payments</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Pay your bills, recharge mobiles, and manage all your utility payments from one single platform. Fast, secure, and hassle-free.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Instant Processing
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-tower-cell"></i> All Operators
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Secure Payments
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>One Platform for All Your Bill Payments</h2>
          <p>TrueCred Loan Expert makes it easy to handle all your recharge and bill payment needs in one place. Whether it's mobile recharge, electricity bills, DTH, FASTag, or loan EMI payments — we've got you covered with instant processing and secure transactions.</p>
          <p>Enjoy the convenience of paying all your bills without switching between multiple apps. Our platform supports all major operators and billers across India, ensuring you never miss a payment.</p>

          <!-- Products Grid -->
          <h3>Our Services</h3>
          <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); margin: 24px 0 40px;">
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-mobile-screen-button"></i></div>
              <h3>Mobile Recharge</h3>
              <p>Prepaid &amp; postpaid recharge for all operators including Jio, Airtel, Vi, BSNL.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Recharge Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></div>
              <h3>Electricity Bill</h3>
              <p>Pay electricity bills for all state boards and private distributors instantly.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Pay Bill <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-satellite-dish"></i></div>
              <h3>DTH Recharge</h3>
              <p>Recharge your DTH connection — Tata Play, Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Recharge Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-road"></i></div>
              <h3>FASTag Recharge</h3>
              <p>Quick FASTag recharge for all banks. Never worry about toll payments again.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Recharge Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-fire-flame-simple"></i></div>
              <h3>LPG Gas Booking</h3>
              <p>Book your LPG cylinder online — HP Gas, Bharat Gas, Indane Gas supported.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Book Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
              <h3>Loan EMI Payment</h3>
              <p>Pay your loan EMIs on time for all major banks and NBFCs from one place.</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Pay EMI <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- How It Works -->
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <p>Complete your bill payments in just 4 simple steps.</p>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Select Service</h4>
              <p>Choose the type of bill or recharge you want to make.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Enter Details</h4>
              <p>Provide your mobile number, account number, or consumer ID.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Make Payment</h4>
              <p>Pay securely via UPI, net banking, debit/credit card, or wallet.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Get Confirmation</h4>
              <p>Receive instant confirmation via SMS and email notification.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Supported Operators -->
          <h2>Supported Operators &amp; Billers</h2>
          <p>We support a wide range of operators and billers across India to ensure maximum coverage for all your payment needs.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Mobile Operators:</strong> Jio, Airtel, Vi (Vodafone Idea), BSNL, MTNL</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>DTH Providers:</strong> Tata Play, Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct, D2H</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Electricity Boards:</strong> All state electricity boards and private distributors</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>FASTag:</strong> All major bank FASTags including SBI, HDFC, ICICI, Axis, Paytm</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>LPG Gas:</strong> HP Gas, Bharat Gas, Indane Gas</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Loan EMI:</strong> All major banks and NBFCs including SBI, HDFC, ICICI, Bajaj Finserv, Tata Capital</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Page CTA -->
          <div class="page-cta">
            <div>
              <h3>Looking for a Loan Instead?</h3>
              <p>Compare and apply for personal loans, home loans, and more from top lenders.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/pages/personal-loan" class="btn btn-outline">Check Offers <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <!-- Quick Recharge Form -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-bolt" style="color: var(--primary); margin-right: 6px;"></i> Quick Recharge</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Service Type</option>
                  <option value="mobile">Mobile Recharge</option>
                  <option value="electricity">Electricity Bill</option>
                  <option value="dth">DTH Recharge</option>
                  <option value="fastag">FASTag Recharge</option>
                  <option value="lpg">LPG Gas Booking</option>
                  <option value="emi">Loan EMI Payment</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile / Account Number">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="number" class="form-input" placeholder="Amount (₹)">
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                Recharge Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/personal-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Personal Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/investments"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Investments</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">FAQs</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Find answers to common questions about recharge and bill payments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Is it safe to make bill payments on TrueCred?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Absolutely. TrueCred Loan Expert uses bank-grade SSL encryption and is ISO/IEC 27001:2022 certified. All payment transactions are processed through secure payment gateways with 256-bit encryption. Your financial data is never stored on our servers, ensuring complete safety and privacy.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How long does it take for a recharge to get processed?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Most recharges and bill payments are processed instantly — within a few seconds of successful payment. In rare cases, it may take up to 30 minutes due to operator-side delays. If your recharge is not processed within 30 minutes, please contact our support team for assistance.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Which payment methods are accepted?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              We accept all major payment methods including UPI (Google Pay, PhonePe, Paytm), net banking from all major banks, debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Rupay), credit cards, and popular digital wallets. You can choose whichever method is most convenient for you.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What happens if my payment fails but money is debited?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              If your payment fails but the amount has been debited from your account, the money will be automatically refunded to your source account within 5-7 business days. If you do not receive the refund within this timeframe, please contact our support team with your transaction reference number for expedited resolution.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I set up auto-pay for recurring bills?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, we support auto-pay for select billers including electricity, mobile postpaid, and DTH connections. You can set up auto-pay through UPI mandate or e-NACH. Once set up, your bills will be automatically paid on the due date, ensuring you never miss a payment. You'll receive notifications before each auto-debit.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
